quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini Й—i, O Wi'i: Miin Mi waЙ—at ma gardotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“e Ibarahiima wi'i waЙ— Й—um kadi e Й“esngu am O wi'i tooГұooЙ“e Й“e keЙ“ataa fodoore Am"
  2,125,Nde Min mbaЙ—i suudu ndu ruttorde yimЙ“e e hoolaare njokito-Й—ee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde Min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo Й“e laЙ“Й“in suudu Amngam wanngotooЙ“e e ufnotooЙ“e e juulooЙ“e
  2,126,Nde Ibrahiima wi'i jooma am waЙ—an min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi njeЙ—aa yimЙ“e mum Й“iЙ“Й“e leЙ—Й—e wonande goonЙ—inЙ“e Alla e Гұande wattan O wi'i kala jedduЙ—o Mi weltina mo seeЙ—a fawoo heen Mi faana mon lette jayngol e battane bonЙ—e
  2,127,Nde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila Й“amtatnoo dosЙ—e suudu ndu eЙ“e mbi'a Jooma amen jaЙ“an min ko Aan woni nanoowo ngannduЙ—o fof
  2,128,Jooma amen waЙ— min jaЙ“anЙ“e Ma mbaЙ—aa e Й“esngu amen leГұol juulЙ“e yo A hollu min tinndinorЙ—e dewe amen njaafo-ЖҠaa min ko Aan tigi woni jaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o
  2,129,"Jooma amen waЙ— e maЙ“Й“e nulaaЙ—o ombo janngana Й“e aayeeje Maa o anndina Й“e Kur'aana Maa o e sunna o, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e ko Aaan tigi woni jaaliiЙ—o ГұeeГұЙ—uЙ—o"
  2,130,Alaa Й—uurnotooЙ—o (calotooЙ—o) laawol Ibrahiima sonaa mbo fittaandu mum Й—aayi nganndee Min cuЙ“iima mo e aduna kanko o jeyaa ko e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e to laakara
  2,131,Nde Jooma mum wii Mo jaЙ“anAm ngonaa juulЙ—o o wi'i mi jaЙ“anii Jooma binnde Й—e
  2,132,"Ibrahiima tinndini Й“iЙ“Й“e mum, Yaakuub kadi waЙ—i noon, onon Й“iЙ“Й“e am Alla suЙ“aniima on diine Й—e taa maayee sonaa ko on juulЙ“e"
  2,133,Mbela on ceediima nde maayde arani Yaakuuba nde o wii Й“iЙ“Й“e mum Й“ee holko ndewoton caggal amЙ“e mbii min ndewan deweteeЙ—o maa e deweteeЙ—o baabiraaЙ“e maa Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak deweteeЙ—o gooto minen ko oon min njebbilanii
  2,134,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol fagginoo, onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo"
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbii ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wii: -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko e diine Ibrahiima peewЙ— Й—e o jeyanooka e sirkuЙ“e Й“e"
  2,136,Mbi'ee min ngoonЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaaЙ“e Й“ee okka iwde e joomiraawo maЙ“Й“e min ceerndataa hay gooto e maЙ“Й“e ko kamЙ“e min njebbilanii
  2,137,So tawii Й“e ngoonЙ—inii wano ko ngoonЙ—in-Й—on ko ndeen tawa Й“e peewii so Й“e Й—uurniima ndeen Й“e ngoni ko e luutndaade maa Alla suran ma Й“e ko Kanko woni nanoowo ngannduЙ—o fof
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaЕӢkooje alaa diine baaЙ—e no diine Alla Й—e, minen ko Kanko min ndewata"
  2,139,"Wii mbela on njeddondirat e amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joomiroowo men, min keЙ“at golle amen keЙ“on golle mon minen ko Kanko min laaЙ“anta"
  2,140,"Mbela on njiЙ— wiide wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat Й“e ngonndoo ko yahudeeЙ“e maa nasaaraЙ“e, wii mbela ko onon Й“uri anndude Alla hol mbo Й“uri tooГұe oon cuuЙ—oowo seedanfaagu iwde e Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko Й“e ngollata ko"
  2,141,"Ngool ko leГұol jawtungol engol heЙ“a ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a ko paggi-Й—on on naamnetaake ko Й“e ngollatnoo"